Give Your Armchairs And Sofas A Quick Makeover


Redecorate your living room without spending a lot or working too much. Extra covers give your furniture a makeover while making the originals last longer. Put them up on your sofas, armchairs, or chaise lounges and take them off when its time to wash - worrying about stains is a thing of the past. Available in different colours and materials, like the chenille VIMLE, yarn-dyed SDERHAMN, or quilted LYCKSELE, these extra covers turn your sofas and armchairs from regular to exciting. Weve got extra seat cushions to keep your armchairs cosy too.
